law.text: If an instrument contains contradictory terms, typewritten terms prevail over printed terms, handwritten terms prevail over both, and words prevail over numbers.
law.history: Repealed and reenacted 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 14, effective January 1, 1997. -- Created 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 77, sec. 3-114, effective July 1, 1960.
